column5: This just release last week, you must have Adobe Acrobat to download the article which is found at http://www.fisheries.org/fisheries/F0201/F02016-17.PDF. Also, new limits in North-Eastern Ontario for walleye and pike:Walleye limit- 4 in one day, size limits, zero between 16.1" and 22" and only one greater than 22" Pike- Still 6 in one day Size limit- only two greater than 24" of which only one may be greater than 34" in length.
